{"tid":1559390,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖]新蒲崗星君冰廳個廚房光頭肥佬藍撚到仆街","createTime":"2019-09-10T19:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:26:13.000Z","uid":3523,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"69019c8ff92c2fa2cc159d236ac01c59ddac0c5c","tid":1559390,"uid":3523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T19:21:06.000Z","msg":"喺附近做野，有次入去食飯，大概2點左右， 就會有條光頭肥佬出黎樓面坐低食飯。<br />\n<br />\n通常間野播住cctvb新聞台，小弟埋單前聽到佢係到屌手足係搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地鐵有人搞不合作運動又話會一拳打柒啲人<br />\n中學生人鏈又話唔知佢地啲家長點教仔女<br />\n<br />\n依家我就唔會再去依間食啦 希望各位留意下依間野，罷食！ 想屌嘅入去屌撚埋個光頭肥佬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9yoOwmn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9yoOwmn.png&h=736c2595&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"429ec14916f8f35e74401af8519c8277745ae22a","tid":1559390,"uid":3523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T19:31:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d10266b7ade768b68712d467a1fe0c49435198","tid":1559390,"uid":200321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T20:37:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f84a715599d419970a685e3e9c6cff9312513425","tid":1559390,"uid":13503,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T22:11:03.000Z","msg":"其實好多40以上廚房佬都係藍，因為佢哋成日北上飲飲食食叫雞直落，所以唔覺得中國政府有乜問題，亦都認為送中條例唔關自己事"},{"pid":"455de7f1596d3437decd705ca78643638d7ef2f4","tid":1559390,"uid":266298,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T22:13:25.000Z","msg":"好撚多茶記啲廢老都話打死班𡃁仔就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde46aa63591dca43b72d22982e1aab2b698afa0","tid":1559390,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T22:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src